    b43: Add more btcoexist workarounds
    
    This adds more workarounds for devices with broken BT bits.
    
    Signed-off-by: Michael Buesch <mb@bu3sch.de>
    Signed-off-by: John W. Linville <linville@tuxdriver.com>

